{"tid":2214390,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"羅冠聰入選《時代》周刊年度百大最具影響力人物","createTime":"2020-09-23T08:19:43.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-23T08:24:20.000Z","uid":225931,"like":3,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"4a688f8443ef45124dd52b76d783805fadef6dcf","tid":2214390,"uid":225931,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-23T08:19:43.000Z","msg":"美國《時代》周刊公布由編輯挑選的本年度一百大全球最具影響力人物，前香港眾志常委羅冠聰上榜，被列入「先驅」一項。前港督彭定康為他撰寫簡介，形容羅冠聰不畏懼中共的打壓，堅持為香港捍衛自由及民主，期望全球民眾應該繼續為羅冠聰等捍衛香港自由的人士發聲。<br />\n<br />\n現時身處英國的羅冠聰在社交網站貼文，感謝彭定康所寫的簡介，以及各界的支持，認為自己上榜是過譽，但作為對香港民主運動的肯定，則是恰如其分。他又說，大家所享有的民主自由並非從天而降，而是靠眾人警醒、合力守衛。"},{"pid":"c70963982174d9233c34e34c9dac076818828945","tid":2214390,"uid":225931,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-23T08:20:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ff0bfb8a2851e491cbf48f806047540b36923b60","tid":2214390,"uid":25379,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-23T08:21:14.000Z","msg":"期待"},{"pid":"5b0dea474ab08d46f496ab126d6b59902e063de3","tid":2214390,"uid":155095,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-23T08:24:20.000Z","msg":"蔡英文 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://s.rfi.fr/media/display/b2d35154-fd71-11ea-86a4-005056bff430/w:1024/p:16x9/Tsai%20Ing-wenCapture.PNG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.rfi.fr%2Fmedia%2Fdisplay%2Fb2d35154-fd71-11ea-86a4-005056bff430%2Fw%3A1024%2Fp%3A16x9%2FTsai%2520Ing-wenCapture.PNG&h=49afc972&s={SIZE}\" />"}]}